Rating System

As a user, I want a way to rating potential study partners, depending on whether I want to study with them or not.  
Potential Iteration: 

Communicate

As a user, I would like a way to communicate with matched study partners after we both accepted each other.  Preferably it would be a built-in chat window.
Potential Iteration: 

Viewing Profiles

As a user, I want to see more in-depth information on matched study partners.  
Potential Iteration: 

IQ Test

As an admin, I would like all new applicants to do an integrated IQ test.  The results should be stored in the in-depth information section of the profile.
Potential Iteration: 

Accounts

As a user, I would like to make an account.  There should be two sections, one for public information and one for information only visible to matched study partners.
Potential Iteration: 

Matches

As a user, I would like to see a list of all matches when both me and the study partner both accepted a match.
Potential Iteration: 

Rejection

As a user, I would like to see a list of all matches where I matched with a potential study partner, but they didnâ€™t match.
Potential Iteration: 

Picture

As a user, I would like to upload a picture to my profile so matched study partners can recognize me.
Potential Iteration: 

Settings

As a user, I would like to manage settings for my account like notifications and themes.
Potential Iteration: 

Deletion

As an unhappy user, I would like to delete my account, and have it actually deleted.
Potential Iteration: 

Leaderboard

As a user I want a leaderboard so I can compete with friends for most matches.
